body:
Picture Viewer| A simple media player.
==============================

A small application for media purposes. 
**Features**
````
Loads a picture.
Auto sizes based on window size.
Background color chooser. 
````

Currently working on:
Render methods (Redoing so its faster and more optimized.) 
The User Interface.
Audio support.
